text: Jordi Domingo Coll (born 1 August 1981) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed in the individual dressage event at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
